snippet.title: Official Call of Duty®: WWII - The Resistance DLC Pack 1 Preview
snippet.description:
Rise up against the enemy and take back your homeland. Preview the new content coming in The Resistance DLC Pack 1 for Call of Duty®: WWII.

Get Call of Duty®: WWII on disc or digital download: https://www.callofduty.com/WWII
